    "description": "<strong>获取更多游戏信息、游戏反馈请QQ群:196787625</strong><br><br>欢迎来到《沙盒启示录》一款以沙盒为题材的生存建造游戏，带有生存恐怖和NPC扮演元素。在这个广阔的虚拟世界中，你将在探索、建造、交流和战斗中不断成长，发号施令、组成小队、完成任务、对抗敌人以及制作物品。基于沙盒的架构，无论你喜欢什么样的游戏体验，这里都可以满足你的需求！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索创造</h2>在这个游戏中，你可以自由地探索各种不同的地形，发现新的资源，收集并加工这些资源来制造各种物品。你可以建造属于自己的基地，选择各种不同的建筑材料和装饰，将它打造成你心中理想的样子。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/622e2fecc88f74ef3b11f73d4f60b892.poster.avif?t=1681697602\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/622e2fecc88f74ef3b11f73d4f60b892.webm?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/622e2fecc88f74ef3b11f73d4f60b892.mp4?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/ef157d4be9a9f657f47c8a12bfae08ac.poster.avif?t=1681697602\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/ef157d4be9a9f657f47c8a12bfae08ac.webm?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/ef157d4be9a9f657f47c8a12bfae08ac.mp4?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/f9647b120474b14f54a92e57cedf19dd.poster.avif?t=1681697602\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/f9647b120474b14f54a92e57cedf19dd.webm?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/f9647b120474b14f54a92e57cedf19dd.mp4?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗成长</h2>除了探索创造，战斗也是《沙盒启示录》中的重要一环。你需要面对各种危险，比如敌人的攻击、野生动物的袭击等等。只有在强大的武器和防具的保护下，你才能在这个危机四伏的世界中生存下来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/eab994b2c93529e21138eca7998cd62f.poster.avif?t=1681697602\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/eab994b2c93529e21138eca7998cd62f.webm?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/eab994b2c93529e21138eca7998cd62f.mp4?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/9a0bbe16c022f66f4e1d92046bb862d1.poster.avif?t=1681697602\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/9a0bbe16c022f66f4e1d92046bb862d1.webm?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/9a0bbe16c022f66f4e1d92046bb862d1.mp4?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >模拟经营</h2>当你在《沙盒启示录》中建造了自己的基地后，你可以开设商店，销售你的产品，并与NPC进行贸易和合作。你还可以招募NPC并安排他们从事不同的工作，例如挖掘、采矿、种植等等，使你的资源得到更好的利用。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/2c93bcec4ce58d1de395442381cb6579.poster.avif?t=1681697602\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/2c93bcec4ce58d1de395442381cb6579.webm?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/2c93bcec4ce58d1de395442381cb6579.mp4?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >社会互动</h2>除了单人模式，游戏还提供了丰富多彩的社交互动体验。你可以向NPC赠送礼物、与NPC对话交流，甚至可以策划暗杀行动。这些社交互动不仅可以加深你与NPC之间的关系，还可以为游戏增添更多的戏剧性和乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/3049b935d79537879dcea5c57a7c5bf8.poster.avif?t=1681697602\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/3049b935d79537879dcea5c57a7c5bf8.webm?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/3049b935d79537879dcea5c57a7c5bf8.mp4?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >诸天万界(正式版发布)</h2>游戏中的地图将每次进行随机生成。在这个无限的世界里，你可以在丛林、荒野、山脉、沙漠等各种环境中探险，还有高耸的山峰和深邃的海底等着你去发现和探索。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/d34a9277fd80e0ac9d6a3c83e9c04484.poster.avif?t=1681697602\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/d34a9277fd80e0ac9d6a3c83e9c04484.webm?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359680/extras/d34a9277fd80e0ac9d6a3c83e9c04484.mp4?t=1681697602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>快来加入《沙盒启示录》，探索未知的世界，建造你的梦想基地，挑战世界的极限，享受沙盒游戏的无限乐趣！</strong>",
